name: Two Be
overview: As an educator, Steven Davis has discovered that many students have different needs when it comes to fully grasping instructed material. When considering the many benefits integrated learning can offer within today’s society, it becomes clear that it is essential for students to master and fully understand the many subjects they are taught. While a student may prove skilled in one study area, they may have difficulties adapting to other disciplines. In these cases, one-on-one tutoring methods can help individuals find new ways to learn material.
